	   <tr><td colspan=2>at least 95% of everyone that buys a horse actually opts for the 9K Mule, over the 100K Throughbred....<br>Vast majority dont have or will ever see 100K number 1...<br>Number 2, the main reason for a Horse is being able to med while fighting and not drawing aggro giving you around a +5-7 extra mana regen<br><br>No horse is going to outrun a bard....but if your a slow arse warrior used to lumbering along at a snails pace, or guzzling SOW potions. then a fast horse is very nice, and 50-85% run increase is fantastic, and im sure could absolutely careless the bard is faster so what...He isnt a Bard, He is now a fast warrior..<br><br>and as far as speed goes to get somewhere...yeah a Bard can outrun a Dr00d....But all a Dr00d has to do is click a button and port/succor/evac across the whole zone or different zone in a few secs....thus beating the hell out of &quot;Bard speed&quot; by x1000%<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
